at-centre-of-europes-heatwave-crisis/articleshow/131953400.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/40-drown-eiffel-tower-closes-nuclear-plant-shut-france-at-centre-of-europes-heatwave-crisis/articleshow/131953400.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T08:29:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131953451,imgsize-163247.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Charlie's shattered....": Charlie Kirk assassination case takes another twist as Candace Owens points to new SUV image evidence]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131952143.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens claims newly enhanced images of black shards inside the SUV that transported Charlie Kirk strengthen her theory that his RODE Wireless Pro microphone exploded. She said visible white markings on the fragments match the microphone's branding and cited a comparison with a destroyed RODE mic in a YouTube video. Owens argues the findings reinforce her theory, though investigators have not verified her claims or confirmed any link between the shards and the microphone.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlies-shattered-charlie-kirk-assassination-case-takes-another-twist-as-candace-owens-points-to-new-suv-image-evidence/articleshow/131952143.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlies-shattered-charlie-kirk-assassination-case-takes-another-twist-as-candace-owens-points-to-new-suv-image-evidence/articleshow/131952143.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131952143,imgsize-80442.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[xQc suspended from Twitch after FIFA World Cup 2026 copyright claim explained]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949703.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular streamer xQc faced a temporary 48-hour suspension from Twitch after his channel received two copyright strikes. The action stemmed from a brief clip of FIFA World Cup 2026 match footage, reportedly around five seconds long and sourced from social media. This marks xQc's sixth suspension, highlighting ongoing debates about copyright enforcement on live-streaming platforms and the rapid dissemination of sports highlights.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/xqc-suspended-from-twitch-after-fifa-world-cup-2026-copyright-claim-explained/articleshow/131949703.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/xqc-suspended-from-twitch-after-fifa-world-cup-2026-copyright-claim-explained/articleshow/131949703.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:35:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949701,imgsize-655590.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Spanish proverb of the day on ingratitude, betrayal and expectation: 'Raise crows and they will pluck out your eyes']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949508.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-proverb-of-the-day-on-ingratitude-betrayal-and-expectation-raise-crows-and-they-will-pluck-out-your-eyes/articleshow/131949508.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-proverb-of-the-day-on-ingratitude-betrayal-and-expectation-raise-crows-and-they-will-pluck-out-your-eyes/articleshow/131949508.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:11:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949557,imgsize-104830.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kylian Mbappé’s France vs Iraq World Cup highlight gets xQc suspended as FIFA issues copyright strike]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949495.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[xQc received a temporary Twitch suspension after showing a five-second Kylian Mbappé highlight from France’s World Cup match against Iraq. He said FIFA filed the DMCA claim, leading to a 24-48 hour ban. His explanation was later supported by reports from Dexerto, Sportskeeda and discussions on Reddit, all pointing to the same copyright issue.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kylian-mbapps-france-vs-iraq-world-cup-highlight-gets-xqc-suspended-as-fifa-issues-copyright-strike/articleshow/131949495.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kylian-mbapps-france-vs-iraq-world-cup-highlight-gets-xqc-suspended-as-fifa-issues-copyright-strike/articleshow/131949495.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:04:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949467,imgsize-74302.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: IShowSpeed loses it as Cristiano Ronaldo scores his first goal of the 2026 World Cup]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949341.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Cristiano Ronaldo's first goal at the 2026 FIFA World Cup ignited an explosive reaction from superfan IShowSpeed, whose stadium celebration went viral. The streamer's ecstatic display, fueled by his long-standing admiration for the Portuguese star, nearly overshadowed Ronaldo's brace against Uzbekistan. This moment highlights the increasing synergy between online personalities and major sporting events, captivating global audiences.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/watch-ishowspeed-loses-it-as-cristiano-ronaldo-scores-his-first-goal-of-the-2026-world-cup/articleshow/131949341.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/watch-ishowspeed-loses-it-as-cristiano-ronaldo-scores-his-first-goal-of-the-2026-world-cup/articleshow/131949341.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T00:53:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949333,imgsize-580055.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Bank of India wins Rs 100 crore case against Nirav Modi]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949339.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/bank-of-india-wins-rs-100-crore-case-against-nirav-modi/articleshow/131949339.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/bank-of-india-wins-rs-100-crore-case-against-nirav-modi/articleshow/131949339.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:02:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">NAOMI CANTON</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949464,imgsize-57540.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Afghan proverb of the day on why force is overrated: 'He who can be killed by sugar should not be killed by poison']]></title><descrip